        That said, Steve&apos;s conference seems unstoppable now.</segment>
    <segment id="12" parent="64" relname="span">  The
important thing will be, I suggest, to try to turn it from a slanging
match that will harm everyone into a debate about the academic issues.</segment>
    <segment id="13" parent="49" relname="span"> 
Turning the arguments around case studies is essential . </segment>
    <segment id="14" parent="48" relname="span"> Unfortunately,
the DNA case is inappropriate</segment>
